track_notes: This is the shorter track to summit, 2 or 3 cars must park at the begining of the forest road.plenty room for antenna, but there is no cross to fix the mast... Nice panorama to the Mercantour dummits over 10.000 feet

This time i parked next to the old tank from WW2. And surprise, i met YO9FWD that was going to activate the same summit.
Funny
I wanted to try a new way to Maouné, this was not a good idea... I chessed for i is hard, long and also weather was bad. Do not try this side to climb to F/AM-350 Mont Maouné
track_title: Do not try the Kylian Jornet's track

track_notes: Done in summertime, this is an easy walk, just a bit long. There is much room on summit for antenna. Since 2024, NO more cross or other thing to fix mast (just few trees down the edge). Take some water, even if there is a source, where TICKS are waiting for you!!!
